  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Incredibly addictive, dynamic blocky cars that give you a lot of positive emotions! In Pixel Car Racer you have to take part in a breathtaking racer car game where you have to rush along a track full of secrets, obstacles, bonuses, jumps and finish first.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏁 Action-filled Race Tracks</strong></h2>Explore challenging tracks, crash every voxel, become faster than opponents and conquer the title of Champion in pixel car racer!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/66564748db7180091b6bb07c8c7494cd.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/66564748db7180091b6bb07c8c7494cd.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/66564748db7180091b6bb07c8c7494cd.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥 Unique Voxel Destruction</strong></h2>Voxel crash system that affects blocky cars performance and wrecks the car apart block by block to crash block car racer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/93a9a235c7016395b667a15af5d40e41.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/93a9a235c7016395b667a15af5d40e41.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/93a9a235c7016395b667a15af5d40e41.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 Spectacular Blocky Cars Action</strong></h2>The car race game has realistic physics, stylish 3D graphics, easy-to-use controls, entertaining gameplay and spectacular car crashes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/cba01dfd7420ba6a8d2d439dc4c09a0c.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/cba01dfd7420ba6a8d2d439dc4c09a0c.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/cba01dfd7420ba6a8d2d439dc4c09a0c.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚗 Unique Race Car - Collect All Of Them</strong></h2>Collect a garage full of karts, monster trucks, muscle cars, snowmobiles, buggies, formula supercars, micro cars and motorcycles - every car has a unique voxel set.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/0555af375e2cae5ca9c55ef238aa4596.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/0555af375e2cae5ca9c55ef238aa4596.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/0555af375e2cae5ca9c55ef238aa4596.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔫 Powerup Your Pixel Car Racer</strong></h2>Discover Powerups to use weapons like missiles or shield boost for competitive advantage against other car racers during pixel games. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/9d5ff86b18ab4c1cfa13b880ad34f47b.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/9d5ff86b18ab4c1cfa13b880ad34f47b.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/9d5ff86b18ab4c1cfa13b880ad34f47b.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🚀 Upgrade Advantage</strong></h2>Upgrade race car stats to increase performance and voxel destruction prototype survivability to win pixel games.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Highlights:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Career mode with more than 60 tracks<br></li><li>Quick Race mode featuring every day challenges<br></li><li>28 unique blocky cars with different voxel set, strengths and weaknesses<br></li><li>Dozens of unique power-ups, upgrades and weapons to use during the race!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Incredibly addictive, dynamic blocky cars that give you a lot of positive emotions! In Pixel Car Racer you have to take part in a breathtaking racer car game where you have to rush along a track full of secrets, obstacles, bonuses, jumps and finish first.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏁 Action-filled Race Tracks</strong></h2>Explore challenging tracks, crash every voxel, become faster than opponents and conquer the title of Champion in pixel car racer!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/66564748db7180091b6bb07c8c7494cd.poster.avif?t=1722230949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/66564748db7180091b6bb07c8c7494cd.webm?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819540/extras/66564748db7180091b6bb07c8c7494cd.mp4?t=1722230949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥 Unique Voxel Destruction</strong></h2>Voxel crash system that affects blocky cars performance and wrecks the car apart block by block to crash block car racer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline p